[[image:Fiat 500 SOS Médecins.jpg|thumb|300px|right|'''SOS Médecins''''s car.]] '''SOS Médecins''' is the official [[medicine|medical emergency service]] of [[France]] which sends doctors directly to a residence instead of sending an ambulance ([[house call]]).<ref>http://www.sosmedecins-france.fr/</ref><ref>[[SiCKO]], [[Michael Moore]]</ref> This works seven days a week, twenty-four hours a day, and participates with close liaison with the public emergency services ([[Emergency medical services in France|ambulance, fire brigade, hospital]]), and continuity of care in many urban centers and its periphery.<ref>[http://www.sosmedecins.fr/index.php/visites/a-propos-des-visites-medicales Visites medicales a domicile 24 H SUR 24]</ref>
Its operational concept has been copied in other countries, such as in [[Belgium]].<ref>[http://www.sosmedecins.be/ SOS Bruxelles]</ref>
==Influence== Doctors of [[London]], [[New York City|New York]] and [[Rome]] came to copy the mode of operation of the association. In [[Dakar]] (Senegal), [[Athens]] (Greece), [[Brussels]] (Belgium), [[Geneva]] (Switzerland), [[Beirut]] (SOS Doctors Of Lebanon), SOS Médecins participated in the inauguration of home care private medical services teams.
